a.n: Barbapapa - One Big Happy Family! I (11)

p.k:
The Grass is Always Greener... / When I Grow Up Barbabright coats the house in magic product to prevent water leakage. The next day, The house deflates like a balloon.
A bird builds its nest on Barbazoo's belly. Barbazoo wants to become a big tree to shelter animals. This becomes complicated (2020).
